  "body": "Ensure that the version of Playwright installed with the Nix flake is equal to the one specified in `site/package.json.` -- This assertion ensures that `pnpm playwright:install` will not attempt to download newer browser versions not present in the Nix image, fixing the startup script and reducing the startup time, as `pnpm playwright:install` will not download or install anything.\n\nWe also pre-install the required Playwright web browsers in the dogfood Dockerfile. This change prevents us from redownloading system dependencies and Google Chrome each time a workspace starts.\n\nChange-Id: I8cc78e842f7d0b1d2a90a4517a186a03636c5559\nSigned-off-by: Thomas Kosiewski <tk@coder.com>\n",
  "changed_files": 6,
